* Pass Parameters\nBetween Notebooks
** Configuration
***_ Add under Parameters section
***_ Key-value pairs
***_ Passed at task level
** In Notebook Code
***_ dbutils.widgets.text()
***_ dbutils.widgets.get()
***_ Retrieve with default fallback
** Benefits
***_ Reusable notebooks
***_ Different inputs per job
***_ Environment-agnostic code
** Example
***_ process_date parameter
***_ Filter data by date
***_ Same notebook, different runs
@endmindmap
